#: ../../language/error_codes/E4061.md:1
msgid "E4061"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4061.md:3
msgid ""
"Cannot implement a trait for a type when both are defined in other "
"packages."
msgstr "无法为类型和特征（trait）都定义在其他包中的情况实现该特征（trait）"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4061.md:5
msgid "MoonBit follows the orphan rule, which means that you can only:"
msgstr "MoonBit 遵循孤儿规则（orphan rule），这意味着你只能在以下情况下实现特征（trait）："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4061.md
msgid "Traits"
msgstr "特征"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4061.md
msgid "Types"
msgstr "类型"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4061.md
msgid "Allowed?"
msgstr "允许实现？"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4061.md
msgid "Current Package"
msgstr "当前包"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4061.md
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "是"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4061.md
msgid "Other Package"
msgstr "其他包"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4061.md
msgid "No"
msgstr "否"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4061.md:14
msgid ""
"See the [Access control of methods and trait "
"implementations](../packages.md#trait-implementations) section of the "
"MoonBit documentation for more information."
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4061.md:17
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4061.md:19
msgid ""
"Suppose you have type `A` and trait `B` defined in package `a` in module "
"`username/hello`:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4061.md:22
msgid "`a/top.mbt`:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4061.md:24
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"pub(all) struct A(Int)\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"pub(open) trait B {\n"
"  to_int(Self) -> Int\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4061.md:28
msgid "`a/moon.pkg`:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4061.md:30
msgid "\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4061.md:34
msgid "Now, if you want to implement trait `@a.B` for type `@a.A`:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4061.md:36
msgid "`b/moon.pkg`:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4061.md:38
msgid ""
"import {\n"
"  \"username/hello/a\",\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4061.md:42
#: ../../language/error_codes/E4061.md:57
msgid "`b/top.mbt`:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4061.md:44
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"impl @a.B for @a.A with to_int(self : @a.A) -> Int {\n"
"  self.0\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4061.md:48
msgid "MoonBit will report an error."
msgstr "MoonBit 会报错。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4061.md:50
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4061.md:52
msgid ""
"You can move either the trait or the type into the package that contains "
"the implementation. If that is not possible, create a wrapper type around"
" the type you wish to implement the trait for, and then implement the "
"trait for the wrapper type:"
msgstr "你可以将特征或类型移动到包含该实现的包中。如果无法这样做，请为目标类型创建一个包装类型，然后为这个包装类型实现该特征："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4061.md:59
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"priv struct WrapA(@a.A)\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"impl @a.B for WrapA with to_int(self : WrapA) -> Int {\n"
"  let _ = self.0\n"
"  0\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  let value = WrapA(@a.A(1))\n"
"  inspect(value.to_int(), content=\"0\")\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
